  <h1 class="case-study__title reveal">How a rule-based chatbot learned to improvise</h1>
  <p class="case-study__intro reveal">
    Over two years at KBC, I designed conversations for Kate — the digital assistant
    inside Belgium's best-rated banking app. My focus: business and third-party integrations.
    The challenge that defined the project: how do you blend predictable, rule-based conversations
    with unpredictable LLM-generated answers — without the user noticing the seam?
  </p>

  <div class="case-study__stats reveal">
    <div class="case-study__stat">
      <div class="case-study__stat-number">186</div>
      <div class="case-study__stat-label">Conversations designed</div>
